WEBVTT

00:00:18.979 --> 00:00:21.656
DA. s'iz geven mit mir tsuzamen,

00:00:21.662 --> 00:00:25.047
 eyne, Kune,

00:00:25.273 --> 00:00:29.131
⟨u⟩n s'iz geven Etele, Etke.

00:00:30.083 --> 00:00:32.929
Kune iz nakher avekgeforn in Poyln

00:00:33.660 --> 00:00:35.746
un dortn khasene gehat.

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:40.961
Etke hot khasene gehat in Kovne un avekgeforn in Kanade.

00:00:41.710 --> 00:00:46.732
nor in lager zaynen mir geven tsuzamen. mir hobn zeyer gekhavert zikh.

00:00:47.076 --> 00:00:49.567
nakher, zey zaynen avekgeforn...

00:00:55.125 --> 00:01:00.282
efsher gedenkt ir di daytshn velkhe hobn gekukt vi ir arbet?

00:01:05.028 --> 00:01:07.051
⟨, neyn⟩.

00:01:17.670 --> 00:01:22.389
geven bay aykh tsevishn di froyen a eltere,

00:01:22.648 --> 00:01:25.359
in di brigade, ver nit iz?

00:01:30.293 --> 00:01:34.441
veys nit. mir hobn zikh gehaltn ale dray tsuzamen: ikh,

00:01:34.441 --> 00:01:37.087
Kune, un Etke.

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:38.972
ale tsuzamen

00:01:38.972 --> 00:01:41.560
in lager. un nakher zaynen mir geforn

00:01:42.949 --> 00:01:45.756
aheym, ven m'hot gezogt az,

00:01:45.756 --> 00:01:50.554
mir kenen shoyn forn aheym. hot men undz gegebn, dokumentn

00:01:51.066 --> 00:01:55.987
tsu forn aheym. nor Etke iz krank gevorn, iz zi geblibn

00:01:56.112 --> 00:01:59.177
in Poyln. zi iz shpeter gekumen.

00:02:00.178 --> 00:02:01.356
nu...

00:02:01.356 --> 00:02:03.172
un Kune, ⟨o⟩,

00:02:03.172 --> 00:02:06.366
un Kune iz geforn mit mir tsu glaykh.

00:02:06.793 --> 00:02:10.685
mir zaynen gekumen, hobn mir nit gehat avu tsu zayn,

00:02:10.793 --> 00:02:12.592
vu ibershlofn.

00:02:12.649 --> 00:02:19.443
nor m'hot ir gezogt az ir, ir bruder iz lebn geblibn. DA. dos iz geven a groyser glik.

00:02:19.872 --> 00:02:26.312
zi hot getrofn dem bruder irn, un er hot shoyn gearbet un er hot gehat a dire,

00:02:26.318 --> 00:02:27.538
 a tsimer.

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:29.636
vu hot zi im getrofn?

00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:33.534
vu? in, in Vilne.

00:02:33.692 --> 00:02:34.951
in Vilne.

00:02:35.127 --> 00:02:35.815
DA.

00:02:35.815 --> 00:02:37.629
er iz geven a SANTEKHNIK.

00:02:37.629 --> 00:02:39.795
hot er shoyn gearbet,

00:02:40.594 --> 00:02:44.165
un a, fun der arbet a d- a dire hot men im gegebn,

00:02:44.222 --> 00:02:49.734
un az zi hot zikh dervust fun bruder, hot zi shoyn gehat a ort vu tsu zayn.

00:02:50.398 --> 00:02:53.851
zog ikh, "un vu zol ikh geyn?" zogt zi, "kum mit mir!"

00:02:54.668 --> 00:03:02.137
fleg ikh shlofn mit ir in tsimer oyf dr'erd, un ikh hob zikh gefreyt, az ikh hob shoyn a ort vu ibershlofn.

00:03:02.802 --> 00:03:05.665
o, dos iz geven O- zeyer vazhne.

00:03:06.278 --> 00:03:06.896
DA.

00:03:14.125 --> 00:03:17.030
ikh vil nokh a bisl vegn Shtutgof.

00:03:18.512 --> 00:03:22.471
s'iz geven faln efsher az ver nit iz iz gevorn krank?

00:03:18.563 --> 00:03:19.765
 ve-...

00:03:22.731 --> 00:03:27.642
vi hot ir zikh gevashn? m'hot aykh gegebn a meglekhkeyt tsu vashn, tsu nit?

00:03:27.030 --> 00:03:31.129
dos veys ikh nit, vayl⟨e⟩ mir zaynen geven in Shtuthof in gantsn tsvey vokhn.

00:03:32.181 --> 00:03:33.198
in,

00:03:33.198 --> 00:03:37.963
in Shtuthof, ikh ken nor dertseyln, az mir zaynen ongekumen in Shtuthof,

00:03:38.458 --> 00:03:43.345
zaynen dortn geven poylishe arestirte. hobn zey gezogt, "froyen,

00:03:44.517 --> 00:03:46.918
v- ir zayt di gliklekhe.

00:03:46.918 --> 00:03:48.493
dem bafel

00:03:48.820 --> 00:03:50.327
umbrengen

00:03:50.327 --> 00:03:52.796
di yidn hot men aropgenumen."

00:03:53.123 --> 00:03:55.237
ot dos gedenk ikh. ot dos.

00:03:55.237 --> 00:04:01.604
dortn iz geven oykh a krematoryum. me fleg brengen di froyen un glaykh in krematoryum.

00:04:01.982 --> 00:04:05.570
nor eyder m'hot undz gebrakht fun Lite,

00:04:05.982 --> 00:04:08.526
hot men aropgenumen dem bafel

00:04:08.526 --> 00:04:11.628
umbrengen: nor shikn oyf arbet.

00:04:11.635 --> 00:04:14.919
dos iz geven undzer glik. derfar zaynen mir lebn geblibn.

00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:18.867
⟨m'hot⟩ undz avekgeshikt oyf arbet, flegn mir KOPAenen di kanaln,

00:04:18.867 --> 00:04:21.011
ober oyf di frishe luft.

00:04:21.321 --> 00:04:23.694
un dos hot undz oyfgehaltn,

00:04:23.700 --> 00:04:25.179
di frishe luft.

00:04:26.198 --> 00:04:30.714
s'iz geven kalt? s'iz geven vinter tsu zumer?.

00:04:28.591 --> 00:04:31.485
vinter, vinter. DA.

00:04:31.485 --> 00:04:34.244
geven vinter. zeyer kalt geven.

00:04:34.244 --> 00:04:39.674
ober di luft, di frishe luft, ot dos hot undz oyfgehaltn.

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:48.469
nu, vos dertseyln nokh dem? az ikh bin gekumen in Lite,

00:04:48.469 --> 00:04:51.740
ikh bin geforn aheym in mayn foterland,

00:04:52.725 --> 00:04:56.651
in mayn heym, nor keyn heym hob ikh nit gehat.

00:04:58.328 --> 00:05:00.364
ikh bin gekumen in Lite.

00:05:01.281 --> 00:05:03.873
nit kh'hob gehat vu ibershlofn.

00:05:05.179 --> 00:05:08.126
gut az di Kune hot getrofn dem bruder.

00:05:08.858 --> 00:05:11.164
nit kh'hob gehat vos tsum esn.

00:05:11.423 --> 00:05:14.792
ikh bin geven a iberike, a fremde.

00:05:15.709 --> 00:05:17.408
nit keyn arbet.

00:05:17.548 --> 00:05:20.439
nor ikh hob nakher getrofn bakante,

00:05:20.439 --> 00:05:22.419
un zey hobn mir gezogt,

00:05:22.864 --> 00:05:24.613
"vu ⟨zhe, vu⟩ UNK...?"

00:05:24.703 --> 00:05:28.089
hob getrofn eyne a froy, Khane. zogt zi,

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:34.231
"arbetn?" zogt zi, "mayn man arbet in,

00:05:34.457 --> 00:05:38.467
in, ⟨⟩, shnayderay fun SOVET MINISTROV.

00:05:38.980 --> 00:05:44.204
kum," zogt zi, "ikh fir dir avek. un ale arbeter veln reydn far dir. zey veln zogn,

00:05:44.204 --> 00:05:48.351
bist a orntlekhe, un bist a gute arbeterke, me zol dir onnemen."

00:05:48.351 --> 00:05:49.684
azoy iz geven.

00:05:49.684 --> 00:05:51.714
iz zi mit mir avek,

00:05:52.362 --> 00:05:57.590
un, ikh hob gekent ir man, nokh fun a mol, fun far di krig.

00:05:57.590 --> 00:06:00.168
zogt zi, "Khaim," zogt zi,

00:06:00.445 --> 00:06:04.084
"me darf zen az me zol ir araynnemen bay der arbet."

00:06:05.001 --> 00:06:09.652
hot er geredt mitn ZAVEDUYUSHCHe, un zey hobn mir ongenumen arbetn.

00:06:09.793 --> 00:06:14.748
dos iz geven a groyser glik far mir. az ikh hob zikh ustroyet oyf der arbet,

00:06:14.788 --> 00:06:19.203
hob ikh shoyn fardint un kh'hob gehat far vos zikh koyfn tsum esn.

00:06:20.121 --> 00:06:23.152
s'iz geven a groyser glik, di arbet, far mir.

00:06:23.462 --> 00:06:26.088
nu, un azoy hob ikh gearbet

00:06:26.668 --> 00:06:32.117
biz ikh hob geborn di meydele mayne. az zi iz ge- kh'hob geborn di kind.

00:06:32.117 --> 00:06:35.015
vu iberlozn hob ikh nit gehat ir.

00:06:36.591 --> 00:06:40.871
bin ikh geblibn in shtub mit ir. hob ikh shoyn, bin ikh avek fun der arbet.

00:06:40.877 --> 00:06:45.562
nu, dan iz shoyn geven shver der lebn. mayn man hot zeyer veynik fardint.

00:06:45.687 --> 00:06:50.659
az mir hobn beyde gearbet, hobn mir gekent makhn a lebn, ober er aleyn...

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:52.599
iz geven zeyer shver.

00:06:52.707 --> 00:06:55.536
nor, vi m'hot gekent, azoy hot men gelebt.

00:06:57.280 --> 00:06:58.708
nu, vos nokh?

00:06:58.714 --> 00:07:02.977
ir zayt geven in Kovne? ir hot gezen di geto?

00:07:03.658 --> 00:07:04.926
ve⟨UNK⟩?

00:07:04.250 --> 00:07:06.191
nokh di milkhome.

00:07:07.050 --> 00:07:10.486
nokh di milkhome, eyn mol bin ikh geven.

00:07:10.493 --> 00:07:14.081
m'iz geforn oyfn nayntn fort, bin dortn eyn mol geven.

00:07:14.290 --> 00:07:15.347
nor

00:07:15.437 --> 00:07:16.629
merer

00:07:16.990 --> 00:07:19.852
nit. vayl ikh, s'iz NEVOZMOZHNe.

00:07:19.852 --> 00:07:28.082
dortn ligt mayn tate. dortn ligt mayn shvester. dortn lign, mayn plimenik. aza guter yingl!

00:07:28.082 --> 00:07:31.681
shoyn geven a groyser yingl; er iz shoyn gegan in firtn klas.

00:07:31.958 --> 00:07:34.213
aza, ⟨⟩, kind!

00:07:35.232 --> 00:07:36.711
dortn lign

00:07:37.662 --> 00:07:39.563
mayne ale noente.

00:07:39.872 --> 00:07:41.435
ikh ken dortn nit.

00:07:41.661 --> 00:07:46.869
ot, kh'hob gekrogn a briv fun mayne frayn⟨t⟩ fun England. hert, shraybt zi mir

00:07:47.128 --> 00:07:49.197
az s'vet itster zayn

00:07:49.457 --> 00:07:52.128
a ekskursye in Lite.

00:07:52.128 --> 00:07:54.750
m'vet forn oyfn nayntn fort.

00:07:56.072 --> 00:07:58.951
m'vet forn in ⟨Belorusye⟩,

00:07:59.143 --> 00:08:01.027
vu s'lign oykh yidn,

00:08:01.337 --> 00:08:02.934
 oysgehargete.

00:08:03.261 --> 00:08:06.208
shraybt zi, "dos iz zeyer

00:08:06.349 --> 00:08:09.110
a, a interesante ekskursye."

00:08:09.336 --> 00:08:12.941
trakht ikh, "a kluge froy iz zi, dakht zikh,

00:08:13.234 --> 00:08:17.010
un zi shraybt "a interesante ekskursye.""

00:08:17.010 --> 00:08:20.855
far vemen s'iz interesant, un far vemen s'iz BOL'Ne.

00:08:21.165 --> 00:08:24.281
vos far a interesante ekskursye iz dos?

00:08:24.928 --> 00:08:29.967
un ikh trakht az zi ⟨ken⟩ kumen; ikh ken nit forn dortn oyfn nayntn fort.

00:08:30.177 --> 00:08:32.061
ikh ken dortn nit forn,

00:08:32.386 --> 00:08:34.506
vayle mir iz dos BOL'Ne.

00:08:36.032 --> 00:08:42.062
un zey iz INTERESNe. fun Amerike, fun ANGLI⟨e⟩, fun FRANTSI⟨e⟩, fun umetum, fun der gantser velt

00:08:42.062 --> 00:08:45.274
fort men do in Lite oyf ekskursyes.

00:08:45.415 --> 00:08:49.408
YA ZABYLA KAKOY CHISLO KOGDA ONI PRIEDUT ZDES'.

00:08:49.768 --> 00:08:53.052
zi hot geshribn az zi vet kumen bay undz oykh in gest,

00:08:53.852 --> 00:08:55.432
oyf a bisl tsayt.

00:08:55.776 --> 00:08:59.516
nor tsu shraybn az dos iz a interesante ekskursye!

00:08:59.944 --> 00:09:01.338
vu iz di kop?

00:09:01.463 --> 00:09:03.161
⟨iz⟩ aleyn a yidishe.

00:09:03.319 --> 00:09:05.388
vos far a interesante?

00:09:06.070 --> 00:09:07.481
s'iz dokh BOL'Ne!

00:09:10.727 --> 00:09:16.762
⟨iz⟩ zikh geratevet ver nit iz fun di velkhe ir hot gevust in geto, in Kovner geto?

00:09:17.325 --> 00:09:19.378
ir hot getrofn zey?

00:09:32.344 --> 00:09:38.058
beshas di krig hot zikh ongehoybn un di khavertes hobn mir gerufn loyfn mit zey...

00:09:38.925 --> 00:09:45.503
zaynen zey avekgelofn, iz geven eyne, mayn tate's a yingere shvester, mitn man, mit a kind,

00:09:45.503 --> 00:09:48.285
un eyne, mayn khaverte, mitn man,

00:09:48.342 --> 00:09:49.821
oykh mit a kind.

00:09:50.569 --> 00:09:56.418
zaynen zey avekge- gelofn. vu zaynen zey gelofn? zey zaynen ar- in a shtetl avekgelofn.

00:09:59.850 --> 00:10:02.915
hot gezogt di khaverte mayne...

00:10:05.284 --> 00:10:12.332
eyne hot gezogt, zey blaybn iber. zi vet, onkormen dem kind un zey veln iberblaybn shlofn...

00:10:12.507 --> 00:10:15.083
zey hobn shoyn farshport tsu geyn oyf morgn...

00:10:15.257 --> 00:10:18.659
zey veln iberblaybn shlofn, un morgn in der fri veln zey geyn.

00:10:19.408 --> 00:10:25.966
un mayn khaverte, eyne, hot gezogt, "neyn, ot do blaybn veln mir nit. mir geyen shoyn avek

00:10:26.412 --> 00:10:27.581
vayter."

00:10:27.581 --> 00:10:29.392
un zey zaynen gegangen.

00:10:29.668 --> 00:10:33.948
zaynen avek, zaynen dergangen, biz in Rusland, biz Rusland.

00:10:34.393 --> 00:10:41.694
un di shvester, mayn ma- mayn, tate's, di yingere shvester iz geblibn dortn in shtetl.

00:10:41.785 --> 00:10:44.799
hot men zey alemen oysgeshnitn.

00:10:46.189 --> 00:10:46.959
DA.

00:10:47.404 --> 00:10:50.047
zi hot shoyn nit gedarft geyn vayter.

00:10:50.188 --> 00:10:51.971
tsu vos iz zi geblibn?

00:10:52.990 --> 00:10:55.178
un di khaverte hot gezogt,

00:10:57.512 --> 00:11:00.931
"mir geyen avek. mir blaybn do nit."

00:11:02.794 --> 00:11:04.762
fargesn di familye ire...

00:11:06.726 --> 00:11:08.627
⟨Broyd,⟩ dakht zikh.

00:11:08.970 --> 00:11:11.934
Yokhke ⟨Broyd⟩. efsher kent ir ir a mol?

00:11:11.940 --> 00:11:12.828
neyn?

00:11:14.168 --> 00:11:15.972
Yokhke ⟨Broyd⟩.

00:11:21.593 --> 00:11:24.034
un zi hot gehat

00:11:24.462 --> 00:11:30.598
a yingele. DA. dortn in Rusland iz oykh der kind bay ir krank gevorn. s'iz geven a epidemye.

00:11:32.460 --> 00:11:34.344
iz er krank gevorn.

00:11:34.924 --> 00:11:38.175
un a sakh kinder, hot men zey avekgefirt in BOL'NITSe.

00:11:38.198 --> 00:11:40.183
mit vos LECHenen?

00:11:41.303 --> 00:11:49.430
ken zayn, zey hobn gehat, ober zey hobn nit gevelt, vayle yidishe kinder hobn zey nit gehat a interes ⟨tsu di t-⟩. un dortn oykh nit, in Rusland oykh nit.

00:11:49.842 --> 00:11:52.637
nor her⟨t⟩ fun vos mit ir iz geven a historye:

00:11:52.677 --> 00:11:54.291
zi hot gefregt...

00:11:54.955 --> 00:11:58.999
ir flegt eyne... zi hot gekent z- zeyer gut rusish reydn,

00:11:59.443 --> 00:12:03.571
iz di krankn-shvester in BOL'NITSe hot gemeynt az zi iz a rusishe.

00:12:04.405 --> 00:12:07.639
I velkhe meditsin zi hot gedarft farn kind,

00:12:07.847 --> 00:12:11.958
hot zi ir gebrakht, un ir kind iz geblibn lebn.

00:12:12.302 --> 00:12:16.551
az di froyen hobn ir getrofn, di vos zeyere kinder oysgeshtorbn,

00:12:16.551 --> 00:12:19.417
zogn zey, "vi iz dayn kind geblibn lebn?"

00:12:19.558 --> 00:12:22.134
zogt zi, "⟨nu⟩, azoy."

00:12:23.845 --> 00:12:27.484
di krankn-shvester flegt ir brengen ale LEKARSTVe.

00:12:27.844 --> 00:12:33.730
nor nakher hobn di krankn-shvesters in BOL'NITSe tsvishn zikh genumen SPORenen.

00:12:33.730 --> 00:12:37.147
zey zogn, "ver iz zi? veystu?" zogt zi,

00:12:37.147 --> 00:12:41.038
"vi iz dos, "ver iz zi?" a undzere, a rusishe."

00:12:41.038 --> 00:12:43.177
zogn zey, "neyn, zi iz a yidishe."

00:12:43.572 --> 00:12:45.956
zogt zi, "neyn, s'ken nit zayn."

00:12:45.956 --> 00:12:48.121
az zi redt azoy gut rusish.

00:12:48.499 --> 00:12:50.501
geyt zi eyn mol in gas,

00:12:50.794 --> 00:12:53.893
un zi treft ir. zogt zi, "zog mir.

00:12:55.688 --> 00:13:00.325
zog mir. ver binstu aza?" zogt zi, "ver? a mentsh!"

00:13:00.325 --> 00:13:02.705
zogt zi, "neyn! nit dos meyn ikh.

00:13:02.705 --> 00:13:05.014
 voser a NATSIONAL'NOST'," zogt zi, "binst?"

00:13:05.037 --> 00:13:07.646
zogt zi, "a yidishe." "a yidishe?!

00:13:07.956 --> 00:13:11.359
ven ikh volt gevust," zogt zi, "volt ikh dir

00:13:11.719 --> 00:13:15.037
keyn meditsin far dayn kind nit gebrakht."

00:13:15.533 --> 00:13:17.434
zi hot gemeynt, ⟨zi iz⟩ a rusishe.

00:13:18.030 --> 00:13:21.076
iz a dank dem vos zey hobn a toes gehat

00:13:21.076 --> 00:13:24.921
