00:13:33.673 --> 00:13:35.658
er volt nit geblibn lebn.

00:13:36.306 --> 00:13:38.578
zet ir vi holt zey hobn di yidn?

00:13:41.335 --> 00:13:46.543
ikh bin a mol gegangen in gas mit a shokhnte, un mir hobn geredt oyf yidish.

00:13:46.785 --> 00:13:50.300
zaynen gegangen tsvey froyen, un zogn ⟨zey,⟩

00:13:50.300 --> 00:13:53.766
"OY, KTO VY, KTO VY? KAK VY GOVORITE?

00:13:54.362 --> 00:13:56.060
⟨TO⟩ VY...

00:13:56.083 --> 00:13:58.341
ir zayt yidishe?" zogn mir, "ye."

00:13:58.341 --> 00:14:01.713
zogn zey, "un ir hot gornit moyre tsu reydn

00:14:02.479 --> 00:14:04.515
azoy o oyfn gas?

00:14:04.521 --> 00:14:07.417
oy," zogn zey, "mir zaynen fun Moskeve.

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:13.171
bay undz," zogn zey, "oy, ven mir reydn oyfn gas, oyf yidish,"

00:14:13.212 --> 00:14:14.466
zogt zi,

00:14:14.466 --> 00:14:17.194
"volt undzer lebn nit geven zikher."

00:14:17.194 --> 00:14:19.399
nu, azoy hot gezogt di froy.

00:14:19.827 --> 00:14:21.610
o! POZHALUYSTA.

00:14:22.392 --> 00:14:27.246
ot far vemen m'hot geleygt di kepl, m'hot gekemft, un m'iz gezesn in di turmes.

