az er iz aroys, zaynen di rusn gekumen.

00:14:39.317 --> 00:14:40.998
iz dokh shoyn gut!

00:14:41.713 --> 00:14:43.361
iz men gelofn.

00:14:43.502 --> 00:14:49.996
hobn zey gedarft aribershvimen a vaser. ale zaynen aribergeshvumen, un er nit. er iz nit aroys.

00:14:49.996 --> 00:14:51.765
er iz geven shvakh,

00:14:52.986 --> 00:14:54.738
un er iz arop

00:14:54.738 --> 00:14:56.185
tsum grunt.

00:14:56.185 --> 00:15:00.692
er iz nit lebn geblibn. IMENNO er hot gedarft blaybn lebn!

00:15:00.715 --> 00:15:03.611
un hern alts vegn dem

00:15:04.022 --> 00:15:05.484
firer...

00:15:06.283 --> 00:15:08.015
ir veyst vemen ikh meyn?

00:15:08.494 --> 00:15:11.106
un vegn alemen, vi z-

00:15:11.106 --> 00:15:12.774
vi ⟨zey⟩ zaynen zikh bagangen.

00:15:13.033 --> 00:15:19.220
az di ershte... vi ruft zikh dos on, vu me patert oyset mentshn, vu me farbrent?

00:15:19.463 --> 00:15:23.037
hot, hot men dokh dortn in Rusland oysgestroyet,

00:15:23.037 --> 00:15:26.007
un Hitler hot zikh fun zey opgelernt,

00:15:26.007 --> 00:15:27.979
un dos oykh gestroyet.

00:15:28.660 --> 00:15:29.970
POZHALUYSTA.

00:15:30.162 --> 00:15:32.571
un mentshn hobn geleygt di kep

00:15:32.571 --> 00:15:33.496
bay zey.

00:15:36.999 --> 00:15:43.102
 mayne a kuzine, eyne iz zeks yor gezesn, un nokh eyne iz gezesn finf yor,

00:15:43.102 --> 00:15:46.103
un der shvesterkind, ot der, fuftsn yor.

00:15:46.935 --> 00:15:48.481
fuftsn yor.

00:15:48.927 --> 00:15:50.271
a idyot!

00:15:50.597 --> 00:15:52.982
mit a tshemodan literatur

00:15:52.982 --> 00:15:54.591
iz er arayn

00:15:55.035 --> 00:15:56.649
bay di soldatn.

00:15:57.313 --> 00:16:00.074
hot er gehat VOENNYY SUD.

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:03.365
an ersht hot men im gegebn eybike.

00:16:03.473 --> 00:16:06.369
nakher hot men ⟨im⟩ farbitn oyf fuftsn yor.

00:16:06.477 --> 00:16:10.920
er iz oysgezesn di fuftsn yor, ober er iz geven halb meshuge.

00:16:10.920 --> 00:16:15.582
er hot zikh dortn geshnitn di venes. er hot nit gekent oyshaltn.

00:16:16.669 --> 00:16:17.523
nu?

00:16:17.631 --> 00:16:18.907
far vemen?

00:16:19.116 --> 00:16:20.966
freg ikh aykh, far vemen?

00:16:24.381 --> 00:16:30.602
ikh halt az di kluge flegn nit geyn mit UNK literatur tshemodanes.

00:16:30.945 --> 00:16:35.495
di kluge flegn nit geyn oyf keyn arbet. ikh hob dos shoyn aroysgezen.

00:16:39.602 --> 00:16:43.038
ikh fleg nor geyn... nu, fleg oykhet

00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.962
farshpreytn.

00:16:47.803 --> 00:16:51.476
nor mir flegn geyn merstns, makhn zamlungen.

00:16:51.769 --> 00:16:54.210
DA. klaybn far di

00:16:54.368 --> 00:16:55.560
linke,

00:16:55.684 --> 00:16:57.281
far di gez⟨ets⟩ene.

00:16:57.721 --> 00:17:00.020
ven iz dos geven?

00:17:00.544 --> 00:17:02.310
s'iz geven...

00:17:07.377 --> 00:17:10.341
geven mistom⟨e⟩ in akht un draysikstn yor.

00:17:12.103 --> 00:17:15.728
bin dokh eyn mol gezesn. hob ikh gehat a khoydesh.

00:17:15.728 --> 00:17:19.691
a tsveytn mol hot men mir gegebn dray monat.

00:17:20.810 --> 00:17:23.369
un nakher hob ikh zikh batrakht...

00:17:24.861 --> 00:17:28.804
mayne khavertes, zey, keyne⟨r⟩ geyen nit.

00:17:29.097 --> 00:17:30.933
hob zikh batrakht.

00:17:30.933 --> 00:17:36.211
a tsveytn mol hot men mir gegebn dray monat, un a dritn mol hot men mir gegebn a yor.

00:17:36.707 --> 00:17:42.135
kler ikh, "ikh'l darfn opzitsn a yor, un nit arbetn, un in shtub

00:17:42.411 --> 00:17:44.548
vel ikh nit kenen helfn."

00:17:44.723 --> 00:17:47.130
kler ikh, "tor ikh dos nit ton."

00:17:47.507 --> 00:17:50.508
hob ikh zikh dos batrakht, ⟨az ikh'l⟩ aroysgeyn,

00:17:50.508 --> 00:17:52.015
mer gey ikh nit.

00:17:54.004 --> 00:17:56.405
iz men glaykh gekumen mir rufn,

00:17:56.405 --> 00:17:59.484
zog ikh, "neyn. mer gey ikh nit. un ikh'l nit geyn."

00:18:00.923 --> 00:18:04.174
vi hot zikh ongerufn ayer organizatsye?

00:18:05.833 --> 00:18:06.940
⟨MOPA⟩.

00:18:08.635 --> 00:18:11.042
