00:18:11.841 --> 00:18:13.151
mit vos?

00:18:13.427 --> 00:18:16.019
dos, mir flegn geyn oyf zamlungen,

00:18:16.093 --> 00:18:19.159
baym f- in di fabrikn,

00:18:22.607 --> 00:18:24.963
oyf rayone zamlungen.

00:18:25.425 --> 00:18:29.941
mir zaynen eyn mol arayn in a shtub, un dortn hot gelebt a militsyoner.

00:18:30.015 --> 00:18:30.836
nu?

00:18:31.247 --> 00:18:35.460
iz er aroys, un er hot undz shoyn gehit, vu mir geyen.

00:18:36.563 --> 00:18:38.970
mir zaynen gegangen shtub tsu shtub.

00:18:39.382 --> 00:18:41.669
un vos hot ir dortn geton?

00:18:41.639 --> 00:18:42.430
ha?

00:18:43.178 --> 00:18:45.789
