00:18:45.793 --> 00:18:48.149
mir hobn gebetn hilf

00:18:48.291 --> 00:18:50.445
far di vos zey zitsn,

00:18:50.805 --> 00:18:52.402
me zol gebn hilf.

00:18:53.472 --> 00:19:01.467
zaynen mir ⟨eyn, a,⟩ gegangen un nokh dem zaynen mir aroys fun a shtub. mir hobn gedarft aropgeyn di trepelekh. iz er tsu, der militsyoner:

00:19:01.467 --> 00:19:03.607
"⟨EINAM, SESERYS⟩."

00:19:04.575 --> 00:19:07.851
kukn mir oyf im. "⟨EINAM, EINAM.⟩"

00:19:09.064 --> 00:19:11.943
vayle bay im in shtub zaynen mir geven arayn!

00:19:12.118 --> 00:19:12.922
nu,

00:19:13.823 --> 00:19:16.584
trakht ikh, "mir zaynen dokh tsvey.

00:19:16.810 --> 00:19:18.407
ikh'l antloyfn.

00:19:19.088 --> 00:19:24.476
vet er mir yogn, vet zi antloyfn. vet er hobn eyne, nit beyd⟨n⟩."

00:19:25.281 --> 00:19:29.632
bin ikh antlofn. hot er mir geyogt, un er hot mir ongekhapt.

00:19:30.208 --> 00:19:33.073
un er hot mir arayngefirt bay im in shtub.

00:19:33.073 --> 00:19:36.159
trakht ikh, "o! ot dos iz di sibe."

00:19:36.925 --> 00:19:38.876
un nakher iz er avek

00:19:39.085 --> 00:19:40.971
zukhn di tsveyte.

00:19:40.971 --> 00:19:43.533
iz zi, di idyotke, geshtanen

00:19:43.928 --> 00:19:46.807
un gevart. zi iz nit antlofn.

00:19:47.337 --> 00:19:49.271
far vos iz zi nit antlofn?

00:19:49.463 --> 00:19:53.186
zi iz, dakht zikh, gornit aza narishe. zi iz nit antlofn.

00:19:54.103 --> 00:19:57.522
un er hot ir oykh gebrakht. ikh ze, er firt ir oykh arayn.

00:19:57.715 --> 00:19:58.671
nu?

00:20:04.836 --> 00:20:07.132
m'hot aykh gemishpet nokh dos?

00:20:07.070 --> 00:20:07.668
ha?

00:20:07.781 --> 00:20:10.129
m'hot aykh gemishpet nokh dos?

00:20:10.064 --> 00:20:11.697
vart, vart, ikh her nit.

00:20:12.008 --> 00:20:15.360
m'hot aykh gemishpet? a sud iz geven?

00:20:15.338 --> 00:20:17.486
nu, KA- vi meynt ir?

00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:21.755
nu, dos iz shoyn geven di ⟨administrativ⟩.

00:20:22.065 --> 00:20:23.277
di ⟨administrativ⟩.

00:20:23.277 --> 00:20:26.902
a khoydesh oder dray, dos iz, di ⟨administrativ⟩.

00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:28.168
ober

00:20:29.524 --> 00:20:32.387
ven me khapt bayn oyfhengen a plakat,

00:20:32.680 --> 00:20:36.336
bayn farshpreytn literaturn, hot men zeks yor.

00:20:38.586 --> 00:20:40.498
hob ikh getrakht

00:20:40.498 --> 00:20:44.717
az far mir, vos ikh hob in mayn lebn azoy fil gehat

00:20:44.717 --> 00:20:46.731
hunger mit tsores

00:20:46.905 --> 00:20:49.923
mit payn un PEREZHIVANIe,

00:20:49.923 --> 00:20:54.510
un dem tatn un di shvester azoy onmakhn azoy fil fardrus...

00:20:54.718 --> 00:20:59.448
vayl a dritn mol vet men gebn yorn. trakht ikh, "neyn. ikh'l mer nit geyn."

00:20:59.448 --> 00:21:02.812
hobn zey nit gevelt mit mir, di khavertes, reydn.

00:21:03.021 --> 00:21:05.259
kler ikh, "geyt ir aleyn."

00:21:07.054 --> 00:21:08.347
nu, un zey geyen.

00:21:09.417 --> 00:21:11.385
kluge zaynen nit gegangen.

00:21:11.897 --> 00:21:14.675
ikh fleg zen vi me dreyt zikh aroyset.

00:21:15.373 --> 00:21:16.902
un ver s'iz a nar

00:21:17.213 --> 00:21:18.506
un geyt,

00:21:21.178 --> 00:21:23.230
ver UNK zayn nit keyn nar.

00:21:23.845 --> 00:21:28.007
hob ikh zikh durkhgetrakht az merer nit, un VSЁ. mer bin ikh nit gegan.

00:21:30.358 --> 00:21:34.597
yidishe yontoyvim hot ir gefayert far di milkhome?

00:21:34.566 --> 00:21:35.971
vi, vi zogt ir?

00:21:36.045 --> 00:21:38.133
yidishe yontoyvim,

00:21:37.845 --> 00:21:38.628
nu?

00:21:38.350 --> 00:21:41.118
hot ir gefayert far di milkhome?

00:21:41.010 --> 00:21:42.924
nu, KONECHNO.

00:21:43.015 --> 00:21:44.477
ale yontoyvim.

00:21:44.719 --> 00:21:45.421
DA.

00:21:46.727 --> 00:21:48.054
mit freyd.

00:21:49.528 --> 00:21:52.306
me flegt shoyn vartn, s'zol kumen der yontev.

00:21:54.844 --> 00:21:57.971
nu, ikh halt az mir hobn nit merer vegn vos tsu reydn.

00:21:58.002 --> 00:21:59.515
mir hobn UNK...

00:21:58.649 --> 00:21:59.461
emes?

00:21:59.518 --> 00:22:03.511
efsher gedenkt ir velkhe nit iz yontoyvim?

00:22:03.923 --> 00:22:07.595
nu, velkhe, ikh gedenk ⟨n- d-⟩ peysekh,

00:22:08.344 --> 00:22:10.464
rosheshone...

00:22:11.517 --> 00:22:15.525
rosheshone, yon-kiper. yon-kiper flegt zayn a tones,

00:22:15.525 --> 00:22:16.961
flegt men fastn.

00:22:17.136 --> 00:22:19.708
yontoyvim flegn mir geyn in shul.

00:22:19.708 --> 00:22:22.676
simkhes-toyre in shul iz zeyer freylekh:

00:22:22.676 --> 00:22:24.807
me tantst, me zingt.

00:22:24.807 --> 00:22:27.642
nokh itster gey ikh. DA. zeyer freylekh.

00:22:28.932 --> 00:22:30.242
nu...

00:22:30.315 --> 00:22:35.489
nu, me treft zikh dortn ⟨mit p-⟩ mit mentshn vos m'hot zey lang nit gezen.

00:22:37.875 --> 00:22:42.589
nu, az mir zaynen geven in ⟨Karolinishke⟩ fleg ikh fun dortn shoyn nit forn in shtot,

00:22:42.589 --> 00:22:44.598
vayle s'kumt oys bay nakht

00:22:44.598 --> 00:22:46.036
un ikh hob nit gehat

00:22:46.701 --> 00:22:49.022
kompanye mit vemen,

00:22:49.022 --> 00:22:51.650
un aleyn forn aher un ahin?

00:22:51.650 --> 00:22:53.118
fleg ikh shoyn nit geyn.

00:22:53.118 --> 00:22:57.748
nor itster az me lebt in shtot, s'vet zayn a yontev velkhn, vel ikh geyn.

00:22:59.745 --> 00:23:05.067
vos hot ir gekokht in shtub az s'iz geven yontoyvim? efsher gedenkt ir?

00:23:04.751 --> 00:23:05.572
vos?

00:23:05.553 --> 00:23:07.276
vos hot ir gekokht?

00:23:07.761 --> 00:23:08.587
vos?

00:23:07.966 --> 00:23:09.830
vos hot ir gegesn in shtub

00:23:09.830 --> 00:23:11.737
az s'iz geven yontoyvim?

00:23:11.344 --> 00:23:12.429
yontoyvim?

00:23:12.503 --> 00:23:13.259
ye.

00:23:12.570 --> 00:23:16.508
hot men gekoyft a hun un oysgekokht zup.

00:23:16.857 --> 00:23:19.922
m'hot gekoyft fish, ongefilt,

00:23:20.012 --> 00:23:20.951
karp.

00:23:21.109 --> 00:23:24.444
un s'iz zeyer gut, yontev. s'iz freylekh,

00:23:25.733 --> 00:23:27.549
un me est gut.

00:23:28.332 --> 00:23:32.629
oyf yontev erloybt men zikh koyfn, vos s'iz tayer.

00:23:32.905 --> 00:23:34.417
a gantse vokh,

00:23:34.947 --> 00:23:37.050
vi me ken, azoy o lebt men,

00:23:37.050 --> 00:23:38.673
nor oyf yontev,

00:23:38.673 --> 00:23:40.259
dem yontev,

00:23:40.259 --> 00:23:42.959
loytn yidishn din, tor men nit farshemen.

00:23:42.959 --> 00:23:45.369
DA. me darf ⟨im⟩ makhn vos shener.

00:23:45.814 --> 00:23:47.647
nu, vi ver es hot.

00:23:49.071 --> 00:23:50.060
nu?

00:23:51.855 --> 00:23:54.262
efsher gedenkt ir purim?

00:23:55.050 --> 00:23:57.874
purim flegn mir bakn homen-tashn.

00:23:58.318 --> 00:23:59.021
DA.

00:23:59.668 --> 00:24:02.276
purim iz oykh a fayner yontev.

00:24:02.352 --> 00:24:03.071
DA.

00:24:03.162 --> 00:24:05.282
mir flegn bakn homen-tashn,

00:24:05.727 --> 00:24:07.881
un s'iz geven zeyer gut.

