di yontoyvim in geto, vi hot ir gekent, fayern? tsu ir hot gekent, gefayert?

00:24:19.490 --> 00:24:23.878
in geto? in geto hot men nit gekent makhn keyne yontoyvim.

00:24:20.713 --> 00:24:21.484
ye.

00:24:24.171 --> 00:24:27.388
m'hot zikh gefreyt az m'hot gehat a shtikele broyt.

00:24:27.816 --> 00:24:28.552
DA.

00:24:31.630 --> 00:24:34.678
dortn hot men nit getrakht vegn yontoyvim.

00:24:35.055 --> 00:24:38.866
m'hot getrakht vegn dem yontev, zol zikh di krig endikn.

00:24:39.144 --> 00:24:41.833
ot dos iz geven der yontev, o,

00:24:42.092 --> 00:24:44.144
az di krig hot zikh geendikt.

00:24:44.590 --> 00:24:46.659
nor vi far vemen.

00:24:47.155 --> 00:24:51.418
andere zaynen gekumen nokh di krig mit di gantse familye.

00:24:51.711 --> 00:24:54.955
nu, dos iz di vos zaynen aroysgeforn in Rusland.

00:24:54.955 --> 00:24:57.108
in Rusland iz geven erter

00:24:57.108 --> 00:24:59.299
vu di daytshn zaynen nit geven.

00:24:59.608 --> 00:25:00.429
neyn.

00:25:00.672 --> 00:25:02.387
zaynen nit dergangen.

00:25:07.371 --> 00:25:08.377
nu?

00:25:08.738 --> 00:25:11.195
er vil shoyn shlofn; er iz farmatert.

00:25:13.632 --> 00:25:21.574
far di kinder, oyf yontev, flegt men in geto vos nit iz prubirn makhn, s'zol zey zayn der lebn laykhter?

00:25:23.858 --> 00:25:28.881
di kinder, ikh'l aykh zogn: yeder kind iz geven bay zayn mamen.

00:25:29.899 --> 00:25:34.348
un yeder mame hot getreyslt zikh un getrakht vegn kind.

00:25:35.704 --> 00:25:38.752
nit gelegn in kop di yontoyvim

00:25:39.349 --> 00:25:40.575
mit keyn zakh.

00:25:44.125 --> 00:25:47.226
az mayn meydele... shtelt zikh for: in geto

00:25:47.226 --> 00:25:49.243
iz zi oysgevaksn

00:25:49.243 --> 00:25:52.455
biz dray yor mit dray a halb monat.

00:25:52.765 --> 00:25:55.037
un nakher hot men gemakht di aktsye,

00:25:55.549 --> 00:25:56.741
un iz avek.

00:26:00.882 --> 00:26:04.875
religyeze mentshn hobn gekent davenen in geto?

00:26:06.720 --> 00:26:08.317
s'iz geven

00:26:08.695 --> 00:26:12.570
mentshn vos m'hot zey, vos hobn gelebt in shtot.

