fleg arbetn, fleg ikh avek⟨geyn⟩ in der fri oyf der arbet un kumen bay nakht aheym,

00:26:39.981 --> 00:26:42.675
un zikh nit interesirt vegn keynem.

00:26:43.474 --> 00:26:45.746
mir interesirt der eygener lebn.

00:26:48.908 --> 00:26:53.087
ir hot gehat mit vos tsu⟨m⟩ baheytsn di dire?

00:26:55.405 --> 00:26:56.985
⟨iz⟩ shoyn nit geven.

00:26:59.202 --> 00:27:02.959
iz vinter, az s'iz geven kalt, vos flegt ir ton?

00:27:03.842 --> 00:27:05.422
vos flegn mir ton?

00:27:06.880 --> 00:27:09.219
vel ikh aykh zogn vos mir flegn ton.

00:27:09.394 --> 00:27:11.447
vu mayn tate hot gelebt

00:27:11.706 --> 00:27:17.859
hot nokh gelebt frier mayn shvester, di eltere, un zey hobn zikh ongegreyt holts oyf vinter.

00:27:17.983 --> 00:27:20.579
I di holts iz geblibn bay zey.

00:27:20.579 --> 00:27:22.857
flegn mir geyn bay di shvester

00:27:22.857 --> 00:27:27.141
un nemen holts un brengen bay undz, mir zoln hobn tsum heytsn.

00:27:33.070 --> 00:27:36.759
s'iz geven faln az ver nit iz iz gevorn krank?

00:27:40.478 --> 00:27:45.635
mayn meydele iz oykh geven krank. flegt kumen a krankn-shvester a yidishe,

00:27:46.266 --> 00:27:47.812
a bakante,

00:27:48.510 --> 00:27:50.343
flegt ir makhn UKOLn.

